text.tspan: Space Station Mir is the central link of the entre Russian Space Station complex.
All power, energy, scientific, service, and communication command systems are
controlled from a central post in the Mir basic unit. Being an integral part of the
entire Mir complex, this basic unit must be operational at all times.
The Earth weight of this module exceeds 20 tons.
